"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-celebrity-news-1933269-matt-baker-wife-family-ordeal-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Matt Bakerhas recalled the moment he knew his family were \\\"in trouble\\\" after a terrifying incident on the farm.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 113, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Back in 2021,Matt's 77-year-old mother Janice broke her leg after being mowed down by sheep.\", \"from\": 114, \"to\": 206, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 153, \"end\": 159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janice_Soprano\", \"score\": 0.9982598884255949, \"rank\": 0.001743134077002591, \"text\": \"Janice\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janice_Soprano\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janice_Soprano\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the time, Matt was away from the farm and was in the midst of starting up his own television production company, following his departure from The One Show.\", \"from\": 208, \"to\": 366, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 46-year-old's new venture was supposed to be him taking a step back from being on-screen and going behind the cameras instead, until a TV commissioner pitched an idea.\", \"from\": 367, \"to\": 538, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"During the process of gathering ideas, Matt received a worrying phone call from his dad, informing him that his mum had been struck by the sheep and had to be rushed to hospital.\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 718, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Not giving it a second thought, the presenter recalled swiftly gathering his family and animals together and heading straight back up north to the family farm.\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 879, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My mum is the shepherdess, I mean there is no doubt about it, she runs the show up there and I knew straight away that we were going to be in trouble.\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 1032, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We kind of, as a family, had been waiting for something like this to happen, because it was only ever going to be some farming thing or the sheep that were ever going to tell mum that things needed to change.\\\"\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1242, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read More:GMB slapped with complaints as Laura Tobin's weather report sparks outrage    He went on to say: \\\"Because I knew the workload that was up there, I felt I had no choice and thought let us just get back up there.\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1464, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1254, \"end\": 1257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gamma-Hydroxybutyric_acid\", \"score\": 0.9999951012602586, \"rank\": 4.898763719643855e-06, \"text\": \"GMB\", \"types\": [\"Q8386\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gamma-Hydroxybutyric_acid\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gamma-Hydroxybutyric_acid\"}, {\"begin\": 1285, \"end\": 1296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Tobin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laura Tobin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Tobin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Tobin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We put all the animals in the trailer and headed up north.\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1525, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just started to do these changes because we needed to change the sheep that we had.\\\"\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1612, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While having a conversation with television commissioners about potential ideas, one suggested taking Matt's family farm chaos to the screens.\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1756, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Having never had his family on-screen, the presenter insisted he was apprehensive about the idea at first, but that his family grew to like the concept.\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1910, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not Miss:Rebecca Adlington opens up about heart-breaking miscarr